videos.description: With time winding down in the half, Jalen Tate puts the moves on his defender, spins and walks off after sinking the buzzer-beater.

videos.headline: N Kentucky's Tate drains buzzer-beater with swag

videos.description: Tyler Sharpe drains the 3-pointer with the defender all over him and N Kentucky goes up 13.

videos.description: Northern Kentucky knocks off UIC to win the Horizon League and head back to the NCAA Tournament for the third time in four years.
